00:00:42.218 --> 00:00:43.486
Hey, Haruka.

00:00:43.554 --> 00:00:44.723
Huh?

00:00:45.725 --> 00:00:49.031
I never would have imagined
that Shiba would catch on

00:00:49.098 --> 00:00:50.969
to me let alone you, Master.

00:00:51.035 --> 00:00:53.173
To pull the wool
over Tatsuya's eyes,

00:00:53.240 --> 00:00:55.110
you have to disguise
your presence,

00:00:55.177 --> 00:00:56.981
not attempt to extinguish it.

00:00:57.047 --> 00:00:58.149
I see that now.

00:00:58.216 --> 00:01:01.055
I guess I learned
something today.

00:01:01.557 --> 00:01:04.262
So what brings you
to the temple tonight, Miss Ono?

00:01:04.830 --> 00:01:06.700
[Yakumo] You can let
your guard down, you know.

00:01:06.767 --> 00:01:09.806
It just so happens Haruka's
a student of mine.

00:01:09.873 --> 00:01:12.144
I'm very sorry for intruding.

00:01:12.211 --> 00:01:14.549
I saw you practicing
the Mirage Bat technique.

00:01:14.616 --> 00:01:18.023
[Haruka] So, are you entering
the Nine Schools Competition?

00:01:18.089 --> 00:01:19.258
‐ Well, I‐‐
‐ That's correct.

00:01:19.325 --> 00:01:20.895
Miss Miyuki will be competing

00:01:20.962 --> 00:01:22.231
in the Mirage Bat tournament

00:01:22.298 --> 00:01:24.435
as well as in
the ice pillars break contest.

00:01:24.503 --> 00:01:27.742
You're in two competitions?
That's amazing!

00:01:29.078 --> 00:01:30.147
It would be nice if you

00:01:30.213 --> 00:01:31.784
could answer my question
as well.

00:01:32.552 --> 00:01:34.890
Hmm?
Well, Haruka,

00:01:34.957 --> 00:01:36.426
would you mind telling them?

00:01:36.492 --> 00:01:39.198
Even if I were to say no,
you would just tell them anyway

00:01:39.265 --> 00:01:40.501
as soon as I leave, right?

00:01:41.035 --> 00:01:44.175
[Yakumo] Well, since she herself
gave me permission,

00:01:44.241 --> 00:01:47.749
Haruka here
is a public safety investigator

00:01:47.816 --> 00:01:49.051
for the police department.

00:01:49.251 --> 00:01:50.555
To be precise,

00:01:50.622 --> 00:01:52.792
I only recently became
a secret investigator

00:01:52.859 --> 00:01:55.932
for public safety after I
was hired as a counselor

00:01:55.999 --> 00:01:57.001
at First High School.

00:01:57.067 --> 00:01:58.470
[Haruka] By the way,

00:01:58.537 --> 00:02:01.777
since I started studying
ninjutsu under Master Kokonoe

00:02:01.844 --> 00:02:02.879
about two years ago,

00:02:02.946 --> 00:02:05.652
that makes you
my senior apprentice, Shiba.

00:02:05.985 --> 00:02:07.922
If that's true
then your concealment spell

00:02:07.989 --> 00:02:09.291
was quite impressive.

00:02:09.358 --> 00:02:11.997
That kind of magic
is my specialty.

00:02:12.064 --> 00:02:13.333
[Tatsuya] I see.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:15.805
So you're a b. s. magician, then.

00:02:16.272 --> 00:02:18.476
I don't appreciate
being referred to that way.

00:02:20.414 --> 00:02:22.786
[Haruka] Normally my status
as an investigator

00:02:22.852 --> 00:02:24.322
would be confidential.

00:02:24.388 --> 00:02:26.860
I'm counting on you
to keep it that way.

00:02:26.927 --> 00:02:28.263
I suppose I can.

00:02:28.631 --> 00:02:30.968
[Tatsuya] Then,
in exchange...

00:02:31.603 --> 00:02:35.778
If you hear of any other plots,
will you inform me in advance?

00:02:35.845 --> 00:02:36.914
[scoffs]

00:02:36.980 --> 00:02:38.216
Sure.

00:02:38.651 --> 00:02:40.722
[Haruka] Give and take it is,
then.

